<p>图为青岛宜家商场展间区域，共配有40个家居展间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200808/2769fddcbe5b434f8185301afac5794f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
